= <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> and <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> Alliance

With new elections approaching, the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> is likely to be pushed into irrelevance by the surging <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**NSDAP**</span>. In an effort to ensure his party's survival, Dingeldey has concluded an alliance with Hugenberg and the <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>.

While Dingeldey insists that the pact is purely technical and does not compromise the party’s political integrity, it proves to be the final straw for the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>'s left wing. An accommodation with the anti-democratic and "socially reactionary" Hugenberg is widely seen as a betrayal of the <span style="color: #98C22C;">National Liberal</span> legacy that Stresemann and the founders of the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> once championed.

